Clangeddin Silverbeard is a member of the Dwarven Pantheon.  He is called the Father of Battle, and his area of influence is war, especially as a way of life.  Clangeddin's holy symbol is depicted by two crossed battleaxes, and his realm is Mount Clangeddin in Abellio, on Arcadia. 

